/* MARK: - Keyboard Setup */
"Setup Progress" = "Maendeleo ya Usanidi";
"Open Cutling Settings" = "Fungua Mipangilio ya Cutling";
"Tap here, then switch to Cutling" = "Gusa hapa, kisha badili hadi Cutling";
"How to Use Your Keyboard" = "Jinsi ya Kutumia Kibodi Yako";
"Storage Limits" = "Vikomo vya Hifadhi";
"You're All Set!" = "Uko Tayari!";
"Set Up Your Keyboard" = "Sanidi Kibodi Yako";
"Your Cutling keyboard is ready! While typing anywhere, tap the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to switch to Cutling." = "Kibodi yako ya Cutling iko tayari! Unapoandika popote, gusa ikoni ya 🌐 ulimwengu kwenye kibodi yako ili kubadili hadi Cutling.";
"Follow the two simple steps below to start using your custom keyboard. This page will automatically update as you complete each step." = "Fuata hatua mbili rahisi hapa chini ili kuanza kutumia kibodi yako maalum. Ukurasa huu utasasishwa kiotomatiki unapokamilisha kila hatua.";
"**Step 1:** Tap 'Open Cutling Settings' below, go to **Keyboards** and select **Cutling** from the list." = "**Hatua ya 1:** Gusa 'Fungua Mipangilio ya Cutling' hapa chini, nenda kwa **Kibodi** na uchague **Cutling** kutoka kwenye orodha.";
"**Step 2:** Make sure **Allow Full Access** is ON. This lets the keyboard copy images to your clipboard. Your data stays private and is never sent anywhere." = "**Hatua ya 2:** Hakikisha **Ruhusu Ufikiaji Kamili** imewashwa. Hii inaruhusu kibodi kunakili picha kwenye ubao wako wa kunakili. Data yako inabaki ya faragha na haitumwi popote.";
"**Step 3:** Tap on the text input and choose \"Cutling\" using the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to update the \"Full Access\" status." = "**Hatua ya 3:** Gusa ingizo la maandishi na uchague \"Cutling\" kwa kutumia ikoni ya 🌐 ulimwengu kwenye kibodi yako ili kusasisha hali ya \"Ufikiaji Kamili\".";
"**Step 4:** You're good to go! The usage guide is provided below." = "**Hatua ya 4:** Uko tayari kwenda! Mwongozo wa matumizi umetolewa hapa chini.";
"While typing in any app, tap or hold the 🌐 globe key at the bottom-left of your keyboard, then select Cutling" = "Unapoandika katika programu yoyote, gusa au shikilia kitufe cha 🌐 ulimwengu chini-kushoto ya kibodi yako, kisha uchague Cutling";
"Tap any text cutling and it will be typed into your current text field immediately" = "Gusa cutling yoyote ya maandishi na itaandikwa kwenye sehemu yako ya sasa ya maandishi mara moja";
"Tap an image cutling to copy it to your clipboard, then paste it into the app you're using (usually by tapping and holding, then selecting Paste). Apple currently does not support directly pasting an image on this app." = "Gusa cutling ya picha kuinakili kwenye ubao wako wa kunakili, kisha ibandike kwenye programu unayotumia (kawaida kwa kugusa na kushikilia, kisha kuchagua Bandika). Apple kwa sasa haiauni kubandika picha moja kwa moja kwenye programu hii.";
"Copy any text, then tap the 'Add from Clipboard' button in the Cutling keyboard to save it as a new cutling" = "Nakili maandishi yoyote, kisha gusa kitufe cha 'Ongeza kutoka Ubao wa Kunakili' kwenye kibodi ya Cutling ili kuihifadhi kama cutling mpya";
"You can manage all your cutlings in the main Cutling app. Changes you make will instantly appear in your keyboard." = "Unaweza kudhibiti cutlings zako zote kwenye programu kuu ya Cutling. Mabadiliko unayofanya yataonekana mara moja kwenye kibodi yako.";
"Keyboard extensions have strict memory limits to ensure system stability. Images use more memory than text, so we limit them to ensure your keyboard stays fast and reliable. If you reach a limit, simply delete some cutlings to add new ones." = "Viendelezi vya kibodi vina vikomo vikali vya kumbukumbu ili kuhakikisha utulivu wa mfumo. Picha hutumia kumbukumbu zaidi kuliko maandishi, kwa hivyo tunaziwekea vikomo ili kuhakikisha kibodi yako inabaki haraka na ya kuaminika. Ukifika kikomo, futa tu cutlings baadhi ili kuongeza mpya.";
"Up to **%lld text** cutlings" = "Hadi cutlings **%lld za maandishi**";
"Up to **%lld image** cutlings" = "Hadi cutlings **%lld za picha**";
"Back" = "Rudi";
"Next" = "Ifuatayo";
"Get Started" = "Anza";
"Follow a few simple steps to start using your custom Cutling keyboard." = "Fuata hatua chache rahisi ili kuanza kutumia kibodi yako maalum ya Cutling.";
"Enable Cutling Keyboard" = "Wezesha Kibodi ya Cutling";
"Test Your Keyboard" = "Jaribu Kibodi Yako";
"All set! Swipe to continue." = "Tayari! Telezesha ili kuendelea.";
"Your data stays private and is never sent anywhere." = "Data yako inabaki ya faragha na haitumwi popote.";

/* MARK: - Setup Guide Instructions */
"Open Cutling in your device's **Settings** app." = "Fungua Cutling katika programu ya **Mipangilio** ya kifaa chako.";
"Tap **Keyboards** and enable **Cutling**." = "Gusa **Kibodi** na uwashe **Cutling**.";
"Turn on **Allow Full Access** so the keyboard can copy images to your clipboard." = "Washa **Ruhusu Ufikiaji Kamili** ili kibodi iweze kunakili picha kwenye ubao wa kunakili.";
"Tap the text field below, then use the 🌐 globe key to switch to **Cutling**. This verifies that everything is set up correctly." = "Gusa sehemu ya maandishi hapa chini, kisha tumia kitufe cha 🌐 globu kubadilisha hadi **Cutling**. Hii inathibitisha kuwa kila kitu kimesanidiwa vizuri.";
"iCloud Sync is an **experimental feature**. It may not work correctly in all situations, which may lead to data loss. You can always change this later in Settings." = "Usawazishaji wa iCloud ni **kipengele cha majaribio**. Huenda kisifanye kazi vizuri katika hali zote, ambayo inaweza kusababisha upotevu wa data. Unaweza kubadilisha hii baadaye wakati wowote katika Mipangilio.";

